data.description: Investment Opportunity! This is a duplex that had a hallway wall removed to open it all up. Utilities are still set up as a duplex. Each side has 3 bedrooms/1 bath. This could be a duplex or a large, 2424 sq ft home with 6 bedrooms/2 bath with a couple of bonus rooms. Gas service has not been turned on & a/c works on one side only.  Home needs work but so much potential here! This could be a great opportunity for a renovation loan.
